{"tid":1897162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"行政長官 : 仿傚乾隆皇 力數十項抗疫功績 香港定能浴火重生","createTime":"2020-02-25T14:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T16:17:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"128e7b664d2aaf9d3c463287f7d8a17f084c2328","tid":1897162,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥撰文回顧抗疫一個月 相信香港能浴火重生<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥撰文，回顧抗疫一個月。她指，政府工作符合迅速應變、嚴陣以待和公開透明三大原則，指本港除了幾宗聚會活動的組群感染個案外，並沒有出現廣泛的社區感染。她指，為有效應對這場可能是持久戰的疫情，政府會竭力做好10項工作，包括繼續採取圍堵策略、增加隔離檢疫設施、解決口罩等物資短缺、盡快安排湖北港人分批回港等等。<br />\n<br />\n她感謝參與抗疫的醫護人員、政府同事、專家顧問團，又讚賞立法會火速批准防疫抗疫基金，及有業主提供租金減免。她指相信憑着愛，香港不但可以走出疫境，也可以浴火重生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ceo.gov.hk/chi/pdf/article20200225.pdf?fbclid=IwAR0Jgxvg9bC01Np4JTHQTsCz3XNkb8VzpQ8YZrfizPXhDHo797tP-S_kfA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceo.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fpdf%2Farticle20200225.pdf%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0Jgxvg9bC01Np4JTHQTsCz3XNkb8VzpQ8YZrfizPXhDHo797tP-S_kfA8&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=36f5a812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ceo.gov.hk/chi/pdf/article20200225.pdf?fbclid=IwAR0Jgxvg9bC01Np4JTHQTsCz3XNkb8VzpQ8YZrfizPXhDHo797tP-S_kfA8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1267893&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1267893%26csid%3D261_341&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=eb0de623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1267893&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>1.</code>按專家意見，繼續採取圍堵策略，加強公眾教育，呼籲市民做足防疫措施，減少社交接觸，切斷病毒傳播鏈；<br />\n<code>2.</code> 增加隔離和檢疫設施，積極參與新藥物臨床實驗，應付可能出現的更多治療需求；<br />\n<code>3.</code>加強衞生署公共衞生檢測中心檢測能力，配合醫管局推行的「加強化驗室監測」，務求更早發現有潛在風險的人士（事實上，在目前 81 宗確診個案中，有 32 宗是透過該計劃由醫管局主動找出）；<br />\n<code>4.</code> 解決口罩和個人防護物資的短缺，並優先照顧醫護人員和其他在前線參與防疫抗疫工作人的需要；<br />\n<code>5.</code>用好「防疫抗疫基金」的相關資助項目，加強全城抗疫能力，特別是促成口罩的本地生產和科技應用；<br />\n<code>6.</code> 照顧兩批因疫情滯留日本和湖北省的香港居民，並盡快安排湖北省港人分批回港；<br />\n<code>7.</code>在做足防疫措施和減少社交接觸的前提下，調整公務員特別上班安排，以逐步恢復為市民提供正常公共服務；<br />\n<code>8.</code> 協助考評局安全、有序地舉行本年度的香港中學文憑考試，並為各試場和應考學生提供足夠的防護物資；<br />\n<code>9.</code>關懷受疫情影響人士，包括提供電話熱線、支援接受家居檢疫市民、分發獲捐贈口罩給長者和弱勢社群、安排送遞藥物給因口岸管制而未能回港就診的廣東及福建計劃長者；盡快落實各項支援受重創界別及員工的「防疫抗疫基金」項目；及<br />\n<code>10.</code>密切留意各國和地區的疫情發展，以科學為本和專家意見為基<br />\n礎，採取所須的果斷措施。"},{"pid":"4890867c9f4fb2b975e63e03c4c7451c0d53a5c2","tid":1897162,"uid":199957,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"下?"},{"pid":"518a0a7c61dd8f9584c51f6f0fb959a825d747a0","tid":1897162,"uid":273703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"市民回顧抗疫一個月，你乜都冇做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ea9296d3fda09d3149894a8eb20b70bf368d62","tid":1897162,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"好大超功最終使香港走向衰敗既局面"},{"pid":"7c500994e8f0500a21299b4425bb52d712433481","tid":1897162,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"放病人入關<br />\n唔比口罩仲 唔比人買口罩"},{"pid":"f274ea55e0d26e5dc814f7094bbd348f6f533a2f","tid":1897162,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"154748877a5be8caee275f06c4e54f493334615f","tid":1897162,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:19:30.000Z","msg":"喂<br />\n妳仿傚左吳三桂喎屌妳老母"},{"pid":"3c3ccaffadf5c7b256e2aa116395671b0fe746c8","tid":1897162,"uid":26385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2ea9296d3fda09d3149894a8eb20b70bf368d62","tid":1897162,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"好大超功最終使香港走向衰敗既局面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:22:36.000Z","msg":"可能林鄭妹妹真係手足嚟，想香港先死而後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「嗱，學野啦，呢啲先叫攬炒。焦土呀，見到未呀，連登仔！」"},{"pid":"163197c7a7b8e116b8571ff8f8e19beeb40e44b9","tid":1897162,"uid":35860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:22:46.000Z","msg":"成班專家叫你封關又唔封按乜撚野專家意見啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549e27bdf871a59b271b28a4e077dacb88678218","tid":1897162,"uid":326665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:25:54.000Z","msg":"之前份報個回應左未？"},{"pid":"a61db25f6f1b5552fb979cc8b57bd90a69eddeba","tid":1897162,"uid":170285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:26:39.000Z","msg":"屌 放過我啦，聽佢啲瘋言瘋語好辛苦"},{"pid":"63bcc8c1ec1660d3c303cbfd5305c960fe3ea8d1","tid":1897162,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:35:43.000Z","msg":"應該講呢D 佢以上都冇做過先真<br />\n係俾奶共派屌先考慮開始命令D 下屬做<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n民間各部門出黎領功先"},{"pid":"59d42da9d88b0dba4e058a9682b7690ed893a01a","tid":1897162,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">按專家意見</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n班專家condom 咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7341facb8b5280f3d954b7a8e9d7d716597e06a","tid":1897162,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:38:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我覺得佢係想用哩篇嘢回應蘋果份小報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass